  "prompt": "What would be the Wipro joining dates for campus placed 2017 batch?",
  "response": "The joining dates for campus placed students can vary by year and specific recruitment cycles. For the 2017 batch, Wipro typically conducted its campus recruitment in late 2016 and early 2017, and the joining dates usually fell around mid to late 2017. \n\nHowever, the exact joining date can differ based on various factors such as the specific college/university, the role offered, and any subsequent onboarding arrangements. For the most accurate and specific information, it\u2019s best to consult Wipro\u2019s official communication or contact the placement cell of the respective educational institution.",
